"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641145044,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"yGR5dPEyZC-XuJGbrnKiifFk7yVYCGeWh7_3-01CcZg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x361aC8835b618704AD34a965882C2ff037695065\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"e0-wlmIPQrGlMdffvnIUn8RgTXqw2dpyvTQjaLJCmDk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"2goY3_FBpf5KNwfNYHr52kjCjqvqe8mno12QnzP85Gc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"pyWk3xFuQP43Frz0-O5T96ARSKcD6yk0FmbDcEdU7Gc6eOG91-qlRUfuzwzllllJKcxTElMsK9gFA9dwVUVxHw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x40a1f65d712315223ee09e32a7a339c9b56010e3d7bfd244190eb1175787e8b2110080d8790864e4bf768aaf52e6be0904bea7bee779fdabc49049c2a59da7221c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"e0-wlmIPQrGlMdffvnIUn8RgTXqw2dpyvTQjaLJCmDk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"2goY3_FBpf5KNwfNYHr52kjCjqvqe8mno12QnzP85Gc\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi